    <body>
      <paragraph eId="para_1">
        <num>1.</num>
        <content>
          <p>The appellant was charged under section <ref href="/akn/uk/act/ukpga/2006/35/section/2">s 2</ref> of the Fraud Act 2006.</p>
        </content>
      </paragraph>
      <paragraph eId="para_2">
        <num>2.</num>
        <content>
          <p>The sentencing court relied on <ref href="/akn/uk/act/ukpga/2006/35/section/3">section 3</ref> as to penalty.</p>
        </content>
      </paragraph>
      <paragraph eId="para_3">
        <num>3.</num>
        <content>
          <p>A cross-reference to <ref href="/akn/uk/act/ukpga/1968/60/section/1">Theft Act 1968 s 1</ref> was considered but rejected.</p>
        </content>
      </paragraph>
